headline: Investing in energy stocks? One name to avoid & one to check out
summary: The latest edition of Good Buy or Goodbye focuses on the energy sector. Hennessy Energy Transition Fund portfolio manager Ben Cook explains why Expand Energy (EXE) is a stock to consider and Occidental Petroleum (OXY) could be one to say goodbye to. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination here.
